, off Isla 
<collectingMunicipality box="[718,833,441,467]" pageId="9" pageNumber="136">Magueyes</collectingMunicipality>
(Lat. 17.940478, long -67.043068), channels among 
<taxonomicName box="[151,279,478,503]" class="Anthozoa" family="Faviidae" genus="Montastrea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scleractinia" pageId="9" pageNumber="136" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="genus">
